  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nGiven contract A and contract B\r\n\r\nContract a has a function that calls contract b\r\n\r\n```\r\n function foo() public {\r\n        b.updateStuff();\r\n        // Proceed doing other things\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\nI would like a function similar to how mockCall operates, that allows me to test if function a.foo has called function b.updateStuff\r\n\r\n```\r\n        vm.expectCall(\r\n            addressOfB,\r\n            abi.encodeWithSelector(\r\n                b.updateStuff.selector\r\n            )\r\n        );\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\nYou can work around this by emitting events and using expectEmit for now",
